      "content": "sometimes i'm just sitting in these cafes in cities i don't even know, watching everyone go about their lives, and it hits me how much of a ghost i am. like, if i just stopped showing up, if i just vanished tomorrow, the world wouldn't even blink. it's like i'm not even really here.",
